name: tic-tac-toe-bot
description: The rewrite of my Tic-Tac-Toe Discord bot made to be 100% slash commands

scripts.setup: touch .env && echo "TOKEN=bot_token" >> .env && touch data.json && echo "{\"system\": {\"games\": 0}}" >> data.json && touch commands.json && echo "[]" >> commands.json

author: Robert Offord
